In this part, Interprocess Communication:
Assumptions: I have assumed the fixed length of the string as 10(ten).
             
For the various variants of this question, the programs P1 and P2 have been named as,
Unix Domain Sockets variant: Unix_P1.c & Unix_P2.c
FIFOs variant: Fifo_P1.c & Fifo_P2.c
Shared Memory variant: Shared_P1.c & Shared_P2.c

All the files use time.h for calculating the time taken.